This program is the clientside implementation of the GOLIATH autonomous vehicle
control program. It accesses a gamepad and transmits that datavia TCPIP to a
server hosted on the vehicle itself.

Instructions:
To run it:

./Goliath_Client <host-ip-address> <path-to-gamepad>

The default values are 127.0.0.1 and /dev/input/js0 respectively.

